The paper discusses improving relevance in personalized search, which falls under the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category. The use of feature bit vectors and hashing techniques also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also mentions the use of historical behavior to predict future behavior, which involves data management (cs.DB) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
